  <entry>
    <title>Note-Heat-Wave</title>
    <link href="https://lizhengxi25.github.io/2024/02/15/Note-Heat-Wave/"/>
    <id>https://lizhengxi25.github.io/2024/02/15/Note-Heat-Wave/</id>
    <published>2024-02-15T07:11:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-03-10T23:55:55.112Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>写给自己的题解，就叫做笔记吧。既然是给自己写的，自当对自己坦诚与爱。不做过多的辩解，但也要给自己留下一个青春的印记。</p><p><em>(洛谷 P1339 [USACO09OCT] Heat Wave G)[<a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1339]">https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P1339]</a></em></p><p>刚学图论的那段时间，看了许多知乎与cf上关于刷题的建议。众多大佬建议刷题时要少看题解，或者不看题解。做不出来的题就以后再做。D教练也告诉我们：我们现在对于题目的容忍度已经比他那是低太多，一道题顶多4四个小时，做不出来就直接躺平了。他那时侯经常要想一周。其实，就是要自己想，总结出自己的法子，而非纯粹地套用模型。</p><p>外加D教练还没有给我们班讲过图论，我自己的图论题解法都是靠着《深入浅出》、各篇板题的题解外加自己的摸索，总结出来的。各种算法的名字我也不知道，只在学习图的存储和遍历时，学了“链式向前星”。其余的，都是基于深搜广搜，随机应变。</p><p>刚做这道题的时候，觉得这题看着很板，遍历所有的点就可以了。后来发现这题的不同之处在于每条边的边权不一定是1。之前的广搜或者深搜其实有个妙处在于每遍历一层，距离都+1。因此，随着遍历的深入，距离也增加，也就是距离与遍历的深度是单调关系。因此第一次搜到目标点时的距离，便是答案。</p><p>然而，对于这道题，边权不是恒为1，因此，两点距离并不与遍历的深度呈单调关系。于是，我想到枚举起始点与某点距离，用优先队列维护。比如，先将起始点的临界点入队，枚举距离，若有一点正好离终点的距离是i，那么，起始点离他的最短距离便是i，就可以打标记表示访问过了，并将其入队。</p><p>在声明优化之前，先强调一下，对于不重复点的一条路上，两点距离仍与遍历的深度呈单调关系，因为边权不为负数。</p><p>当我们枚举距离时，会有很多空距离，白白浪费时间。而对于优先队列，队首一定是最近的点，因此每次只需要取出队首元素进行延申即可。当遇到目标点时，此时的距离就是最短距离。注意：队列中取出的点记得删。</p><p>附上代码记录成长：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;queue&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;vector&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> MAXN (int) (2505)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> MAXM (int) (6205)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> n, m, s, t, ans = <span class="number">1e9</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">char</span> vis[MAXN];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">VT</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> end, w;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">T</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> name, w;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="keyword">operator</span> &lt; (<span class="type">const</span> T &amp; other) <span class="type">const</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> w &gt; other.w;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">vector &lt;VT&gt; edge[MAXN];</span><br><span class="line">priority_queue &lt;T&gt; q;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span> <span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d%d%d%d&quot;</span>, &amp;n, &amp;m, &amp;s, &amp;t);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> x = <span class="number">0</span>, y = <span class="number">0</span>, w = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">1</span>; i &lt;= m; ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d%d%d&quot;</span>, &amp;x, &amp;y, &amp;w);</span><br><span class="line">edge[x].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>((VT)&#123;y, w&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">edge[y].<span class="built_in">push_back</span>((VT)&#123;x, w&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">push</span>((T)&#123;s, <span class="number">0</span>&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (!q.<span class="built_in">empty</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">T tmp = q.<span class="built_in">top</span>();</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (vis[tmp.name]) <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> vis[tmp.name] = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (tmp.name == t) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%d\n&quot;</span>, tmp.w);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; edge[tmp.name].<span class="built_in">size</span>(); ++i) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (vis[edge[tmp.name][i].end]) <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">push</span>((T)&#123;edge[tmp.name][i].end, edge[tmp.name][i].w + tmp.w&#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;写给自己的题解，就叫做笔记吧。既然是给自己写的，自当对自己坦诚与爱。不做过多的辩解，但也要给自己留下一个青春的印记。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;(洛谷 P1339 [USACO09OCT] Heat Wave G)[&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.luogu.com.</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
